description:
"I have the most important role," Pete said with a smile. "I'm the bottom."
We were sitting around outside, the weather just perfect!
Jake was on one side of Pete, Doug was on the other.
The boys were having a blast and they wanted to try something different.
Pete had mentioned a couple of times that he was curious about getting double stuffed. He'd never done it and wondered what it would feel like.
He gave it a try, but what I think he enjoyed the most was the "train" they did with Jake fucking him, and Doug fucking Jake!
title: Hawaii - Pete, Jake & Doug
